Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(651,554)}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(653,547)}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche-{\i1}sama{\i0} and Droite-{\i1}sama{\i0} are currently tracing Haruto's whereabouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have you found Haruto? Gauche?! Droite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch, which of those guys opened there mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why won't you answer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Answer me! Gauche! Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously because you're so damn annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. We have confirmed Haruto's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he is not under our protection yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Kaito, we will require your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now Haruto is located at\N the top of Windmill Tower in 5th Area…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...along with Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You trying to call that guy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten Haruto's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As he is now, we can't approach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito is the only one Haruto accepts from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only person Haruto will listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Windmill Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's called caramel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's got a magical power that makes you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Delicious...! It's really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto... I'll stay with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he's with Yuma Tsukumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Haruto-{\i1}sama{\i0} wanted to see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mission is to destroy the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I get closer, I stretch my hand out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards that shining light leading towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dream of a world that expands from my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't a clue of where things like dreams and hopes are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I run looking for it, I still can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I have fallen into a gap of truth and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, our grand tale has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's move on towards tomorrow, \Neven if our road begins to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will jump forward, before all my\N strength completely drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The closer I get, the further it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that truth that I must seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's to find hope that we desire from a future unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a heart stronger than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll learn to keep running up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the strength to win any battle, \Ndespite just how weak I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My purpose is to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with these invaluable friends of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of the world expanding\N from my feet with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a good thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy before seemed to know Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(408,493)}"Number 41: Haruto's Gone!\N A New Enemy, Tron"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he was sent by Kaito to pick him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother is... always tired because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, I wanted to give my brother caramel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted him to eat the caramel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he.... Kaito was really gathering Numbers for Haruto's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His reason for collecting the Numbers is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My mission is to destroy the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the helicopter that took Haruto-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Haruto go back home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone came to pick him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was one of your people, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That helicopter before had the same mark as yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything about that, Droite?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we should be the only team out searching for Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lying right to me face, huh? You're in a bold mood today, kid! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow-ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and tell me where Haruto is! Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... ain't... lyin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I returned Haruto already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't got the time to fool around with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little bastard! The mood just got even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are members of the Duel Carnival Operation Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to act like that, we have the right to disqualify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want that to happen, answer honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaito! These guys think I'm the one who's hiding Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were hiding Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I turned Haruto over to someone from Heartland who came to pick him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone came to pick him up from Heartland?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what the heck is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... Who took Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb, Foolma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who kidnapped Haruto-{\i1}sama{\i0}, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said someone from Heartland picked him up. What did they look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean their characteristics! Were they male or female?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a very young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in his early 20's, very skinny, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His height was 185 cm (about 6’1).
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His weight was about 70 Kg (about 155-160 lbs).
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! His height was 185 cm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His weight was 70 kg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had long hair, and his eyes were blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had long hair! And his eyes were... huh?\N What color were they again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...! You messing with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I don't take orders from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite! Are you saying you believe his stupid words?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying I believe him per say, but he doesn't seem to be lying either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be someone else who took Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I gave Haruto away without checking with him first...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto... He's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my responsibility to let Haruto go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for Haruto too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, I promised Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to let him see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! If you happen to find him, please contact us, Foolma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we actually gave Haruto to a stranger when he's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito, why are you collecting Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you acting like the underling of a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save my brother, I sold my soul to the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Kaito collecting Numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has something to do with Haruto's sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what did he mean by selling his soul to the devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! What did he mean by "devil"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now we know that Droite and Gauche are trying to find Haruto as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite and Gauche were either ordered to find Haruto,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or they encountered some trouble, and let Haruto slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They looked panicked, like they were desperately trying to cover their mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only are those two part of the Duel Carnival operation committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are also subordinates of Mr. Heartland, the main founder of this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from Heartland?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid the reason they were searching Haruto must have something to do with Mr. Heartland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's likely that Haruto escaped from the Heartland's security.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Kaito... is working under Heartland for Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,collecting the Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the devil is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mr. Heartland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, But... if the one who took Haruto is neither Droite or Gauche...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. The problem is someone else has an eye on Haruto besides them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start the ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You really are awesome, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You always find me, no matter where I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely find you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So scream all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... it's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally come for me to make Haruto's power mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My revenge hereby starts from this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ooh... that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Astral World!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can feel it... I can feel... Haruto's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This...this is the power I am looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice just now...Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Astral?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to Haruto-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking it. It's Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto is suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This power is magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, give me all of your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon reflected in the water outside the white castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon reflected in the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A white castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Haruto really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon reflected in the water outside the white castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon reflected in the water outside the white castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They indicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon reflected in the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, there's an old museum no one uses around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he meant by white castle, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the moon reflected in the water must suggest the moonlight reflected off the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know the address, let's roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito! Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Haruto is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito... Haruto's in there. There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... because...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do know?! You aren't even his brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, Haruto is in pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kaito, this isn't the time to be arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here. They came a lot quicker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you followed, V?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were going to defeat them sooner or later anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like it matters if it's a bit earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you saying I can't beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito is a formidable adversary. Don't fixate on defeating him so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine as long as we buy some time for Tron's ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! I don't know what'll would happen once the fight starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guarantee their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,III.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Brother V.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they are inviting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! In that case, let's rush right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who gave Haruto to someone else other than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So unless I return Haruto to you safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to meet you, Kaito! I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're IV!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to avenge your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I welcome the challenge anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your anger make you lose focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are influenced by anger, your Dueling will suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I won't use Dueling to get my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kidnap Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He;s still alive, so relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the {\i1}moment{\i0}, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't give him to you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite "occupied" at the moment, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to save your little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do it after you defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... a Tag Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! I'll bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who tried to hurt Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... your souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision. Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone gave me some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I was able to paint a rainbow with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with me suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't seem to grasp victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be having some kind of weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I must fulfill this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I don't mind being laughed at for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's because your limits are decided on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show it, overcoming it to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I'm aiming for the big blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For all of its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of those countless flower petals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They came at the expense of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me being able to reach those heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, even though I lost my way today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still yearn for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to recover Haruto, Kaito and I start a Tag Duel with IV and III.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you do that to Yuma!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without cooperation from him, we can't win this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you treat me as an enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.12,0:24:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I already promised Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.39,0:24:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.25,0:24:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuma and Kaito: A Spirited Tag Duel"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.87,0:24:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heartland City's symbol is Mr. Heartland,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.41,0:24:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so "Heartland's Mr. Heartland" is pretty tedious!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many repetitive matters in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like soup pot, salsa sauce, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.29,0:24:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope King Hope!\N (Literal for "Aspiring Emperor - Hope)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.06,0:24:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it like that.
